	•	System prompt (who GanjaGuru is)
	•	Safety rules
	•	Response structure expectations
	•	Send user input as the user message
	•	Return raw AI output

What “done” looks like
	•	AI responds consistently in character
	•	AI does NOT hallucinate wildly
	•	AI follows guardrails
	•	Same input → similar structured output

What it is NOT
	•	Not fine-tuned
	•	Not memory-enabled
	•	Not autonomous
	•	Not perfect

This is a controlled conversation, not a chatbot free-for-all.

